# Markdown Best Practices

- We use `markdownlint-cli2` for all markdown styling.
- **Always run this command after editing markdown:** `npx markdownlint-cli2 "<file_path>" --fix`
- Ensure any generated documentation aligns with our local linting rules. If errors persist, adjust your formatting rather than modifying the linting configuration.